                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-986" type="given" value="FRANCIS WILLIAM THOMAS"></interp>FRANCIS WILLIAM THOMAS WALDRON</persName>
                  </hi>. I saw the prisoner running. I stopped him—he said, "Let me go,"and put his hand in his right-hand trow<lb></lb>sers pocket first, and then put both his hands behind him, through the rails—I saw Mr. Austin examine the place, and take up this money—the prisoner's hands were in that direction.</p>
